list.lemmaTitle: 墨尔本胜利足球俱乐部
list.abstract: 墨尔本胜利足球俱乐部（Melbourne Victory FC）是澳洲维多利亚州墨尔本的一支职业足球队，现时于澳大利亚足球超级联赛（Hyundai A-League）中作赛。墨尔本胜利足球俱乐部比赛的平均入场人数是澳大利亚职业足球联赛之冠，更屡创入场人数纪录。墨尔本胜利足球俱乐部更于2006-2007年球季夺得联赛冠军和季后赛冠军，成为澳大利亚职业足球联赛首支（至2008年为止亦是唯一一支）双料冠军球队。2009年2月28日再次，取得三连冠。

yingyinNormal.en: You're about to witness a great victory, not only to the Capitol, but for Panem.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们将见证一场伟大的胜利，不仅是国会区的胜利，更是施惠国的胜利。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, the Lions technically won, but it was a moral victory for the Green Bay, Mermen.
yingyinNormal.zh: 技术上来说狮队赢了，但在士气方面是绿湾美人鱼队赢了。

yingyinNormal.en: Not very hospitable, is it? We took it from the Formics 27 years after Rackham's victory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不太舒服，对吧？二十七年前雷汉的胜利之后，我们从虫族那里抢来的。

yingyinNormal.en: We did it, Plumette! Victory is ours! Plumette? Plumette? Oh, my darling, Plumette. Oh, no.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们赢了,普露美！胜利是我们的！普露美？哦，我亲爱的，普露美。哦，不。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd march into hell for you, if I thought there was a slightest chance of victory. But there isn't, this is suicide.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我觉得有半点机会的胜利，我会为你进军地狱，但目前还没有，这是自杀。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I hope you have. And that whatever was clouding your mind is gone. Because I just had to give a victory speech, alone.
yingyinNormal.zh: 希望你好好想过了，也打消了你之前的疑虑。因为我刚才一个人发表了获胜演说。

yingyinNormal.en: We believe we are marching to claim a victory for ourselves, for our loved ones, for our countrymen, for the entire human race.
yingyinNormal.zh: 相信我们一定取得胜利，为我们自己，为我们所爱的人，为我们的同胞，也为了整个人类。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd like to propose a toast to the man whose noble sacrifice inspired our victory, Captain Sheldon Cooper. Hear, hear. Hear, hear.
yingyinNormal.zh: 让我们为英雄举杯，正是他悲壮的牺牲我们才能赢得胜利，感谢谢尔顿·库珀上尉。说得好。说得妙。

yingyinNormal.en: It was them or us, Ender. There was no other way. With this victory, you've won all future battles. You destroyed them. For all of us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不是他们死就是我们亡，安德，没有其他办法了。这次的胜利已经帮你赢得了以后的所有战斗。为了人类，你消灭了他们。

yingyinNormal.en: As the knicks Get a much-needed victory on the game of his life. And he is swarmed by his ecstatic teammates And a jubilant crowd here at madison square garden.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尼克斯队终于拿到了一场亟需的胜利，这是他生命中最重要的比赛，他已经被兴奋的队友包围还有麦迪逊广场花园兴奋的球迷

yingyinNormal.en: I'm very happy to report that I've just come back from federal court, where my legal team won a major victory for Chumhum against these intrusions on all of our privacy rights by the NSA!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很高兴地告诉大家，我刚从联邦法院回来，我的律师团为查查网取得 了重大的胜利，粉碎了国家安全局对我们隐私权的侵犯。

yingyinNormal.en: The people are angry. Nine weeks ago, we had an election in this country, but because two states refused to certify, neither Conway nor myself received the 270 electoral votes required for victory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 人民很愤怒。九周前，我们国家举行了一场大选，但是由于两个州拒绝确认选举结果，康威和我都没拿到270张选举人票而这是胜选的必要条件。
